class ClassLoader

{
6
 protected static $directories = array();

 protected static $registered = false;

 public static function load($class)
9

 }
16
 }
17

18
 }

 public static function normalizeClass($class)
20
 {
21
 if ($class[0] == '\\') {
22

 }

25
 }

 {
28

66

 public function make($abstract, $parameters = array())
198
 {
199
 $abstract = $this->getAlias($abstract);
200
 if (isset($this->instances[$abstract])) {
201

 }
203

 } else {

208
 }
209

 $this->instances[$abstract] = $object;
211
 }
212

215
 }
216
 protected function getConcrete($abstract)
217
 {
218
 if (!isset($this->bindings[$abstract])) {
219
 if ($this->missingLeadingSlash($abstract) && isset($this->bindings['\\' . $abstract])) {
220
 $abstract = '\\' . $abstract;
221
 }
222
 return $abstract;
223
 }
224
 return $this->bindings[$abstract]['concrete'];
225
 }
226
 protected function missingLeadingSlash($abstract)
227
 {
228
 return is_string($abstract) && strpos($abstract, '\\') !== 0;
229
 }
230
 public function build($concrete, $parameters = array())
231
 {
232
 if ($concrete instanceof Closure) {
233
 return $concrete($this, $parameters);
234
 }
235
 $reflector = new ReflectionClass($concrete);
236
 if (!$reflector->isInstantiable()) {
237
 $message = "Target [{$concrete}] is not instantiable.";
238
 throw new BindingResolutionException($message);
239
 }
240
 $constructor = $reflector->getConstructor();
241
 if (is_null($constructor)) {
242
 return new $concrete();
243
 }
244
 $dependencies = $constructor->getParameters();
245
 $parameters = $this->keyParametersByArgument($dependencies, $parameters);
246
 $instances = $this->getDependencies($dependencies, $parameters);
247
 return $reflector->newInstanceArgs($instances);
248
 }
249
 protected function getDependencies($parameters, array $primitives = array())
250
 {
251
 $dependencies = array();
252
 foreach ($parameters as $parameter) {
253
 $dependency = $parameter->getClass();
254
 if (array_key_exists($parameter->name, $primitives)) {
255
 $dependencies[] = $primitives[$parameter->name];
256
 } elseif (is_null($dependency)) {
257
 $dependencies[] = $this->resolveNonClass($parameter);
258
 } else {
259
 $dependencies[] = $this->resolveClass($parameter);
260
 }
261
 }
262
 return (array) $dependencies;
263
 }
264
 protected function resolveNonClass(ReflectionParameter $parameter)
265
 {
266
 if ($parameter->isDefaultValueAvailable()) {
267
 return $parameter->getDefaultValue();
268
 }
269
 $message = "Unresolvable dependency resolving [{$parameter}] in class {$parameter->getDeclaringClass()->getName()}";
270
 throw new BindingResolutionException($message);
271
 }
272
 protected function resolveClass(ReflectionParameter $parameter)
273
 {
274
 try {
275
 return $this->make($parameter->getClass()->name);
276
 } catch (BindingResolutionException $e) {
277
 if ($parameter->isOptional()) {
278
 return $parameter->getDefaultValue();
279
 }
280
 throw $e;
281
 }
282
 }
283
 protected function keyParametersByArgument(array $dependencies, array $parameters)
284
 {
285
 foreach ($parameters as $key => $value) {
286
 if (is_numeric($key)) {
287
 unset($parameters[$key]);
288
 $parameters[$dependencies[$key]->name] = $value;
289
 }
290
 }
291
 return $parameters;
292
 }
293
 public function resolving($abstract, Closure $callback)
294
 {
295
 $this->resolvingCallbacks[$abstract][] = $callback;
296
 }

 public function resolvingAny(Closure $callback)

 {
299
 $this->globalResolvingCallbacks[] = $callback;

 }

 protected function fireResolvingCallbacks($abstract, $object)

 {
303

304
 $this->fireCallbackArray($object, $this->resolvingCallbacks[$abstract]);
305
 }
306
 $this->fireCallbackArray($object, $this->globalResolvingCallbacks);
307
 }

 protected function fireCallbackArray($object, array $callbacks)

 {
310

311
 call_user_func($callback, $object, $this);
312
 }

 }

315
 {
316

317
 $shared = $this->bindings[$abstract]['shared'];
318
 } else {
319
 $shared = false;

321

 public function offsetSet($key, $value)

class Encrypter
8444
{
8445
 protected $key;

8450
 {

 public function encrypt($value)
8454
 {
8455

8456
 $value = base64_encode($this->padAndMcrypt($value, $iv));
8457

 }

 {

 }
